I have worked with this head now for almost three years . ||| 1
We use it in an art repro setup and it is the only way to go . ||| 1
We have to zig-align the camera so the film ( actually BL scan back ) and the plane of the art are aligned exactly . ||| 1
The gear movements on this heavy duty head are smooth and very precise . ||| 1
I could align the camera this accurately with out it . ||| 1
